As stated at the start, this file is released to the public domain.  All that
I ask is that you use it, spread it and tell me how great a program it is.
When distributing this program, please include all the files and don't pass
around modified versions to other people, unless they know that it's not the
original.  If you make any substantial changes, please send me a note so that
I may include them with any future release.  You may only charge a couple of
dollars, as a copying fee, if you really need to.


